snippet.title: Psycho Waluigi - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Credits to Thunder Dragon for this awesome game! - http://mfgg.net/index.php?act=user&param=01&uid=6

Fan-Made Game where Waluigi is the main star in this game! If you want to try the game, go download it!

Download link: http://mfgg.net/index.php?act=resdb&param=03&c=2&id=25698

This character is respectely owned by Nintendo, all rights served. This fan-made game is of course a freeware only for the fans to simply enjoy.
